      <abstract>
        <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>TOPIC</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                From basic system overview, over storage management to keeping
                your system up to date. &cockpit; enables you to perform a
                number of administration tasks in a convenient way.
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>INTENTION</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                This articles is intended to provide a complete overview of
                tasks that can be performed from the &cockpit; web interface.
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>REQUIREMENTS</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                To fully administer the system using &cockpit;, you must have
                the &rootuser; access or sudo privileges.
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
      </abstract>
